node.text:
I am honored fo be part of this documentary, made by the beautiful and talented @jeffwitzeman called “Beliefs & Stories, talking about the beliefs and stories we carry with us that impact us in profound and detrimental ways until we go through the process of awakening to know the truth of who we really are. ⁣
⁣
Featuring Jeff, @_al_boogie_ (Alec Zeck), @kellybroganmd, @dr.cassiehuckaby, @nakedtj_ , (Dr. Tommy John), @yojimd (Dr. Jo Yi), Dr. Christiane Northrup, Dr. Tom Cowan, fenixmeddr (Dr. Carrie Madej), and @xavier.dagba. ⁣
⁣
It is a beautiful portrait of the human spirit and the hurdles we can overcome to find our ultimate human condition—love. ⁣
⁣
It will be available on Vimeo on Demand this Friday, July 30tj.

Or how about the absolute emotional manipulation at the end when the little girl tells her dad, "I love you daddy…thanks for keeping me safe." ⁣I suppose me and billions of other parents were terrible because we didn't do enough to keep our kids "safe" from the flu. LoL.

Health Freedom for Humanity unites people from all walks of life under one common purpose: the reclamation and defense of health freedom. 

We are a community of advocates, parents, teachers, actors, veterans, doctors, lawyers, and friends, who stand to ensure Health Freedom for all people. We come from every religion, political affiliation, socioeconomic background, and philosophy on personal health, but are united in our belief that mandated medical procedures of any kind, medical coercion, or any restrictions on health choice violate basic human rights.

We welcome you to stand with us to protect and advance this right against all past, current, and future infringements, via education, personal empowerment, community support, and unity in action. 

We are Health Freedom for Humanity. 

Join us.

www.healthfreedomforhumanity.org

I broke up with Big Pharma when the lies became too great for me to continue accepting them. ⁣

When I could see the confusion in my therapist’s and doctor’s eyes, they felt so submerged in the murky waters of the lie, yet they could see me dying too. ⁣

When the danger to my life loomed larger than any proposed benefit I was told would happen but never did anyway. ⁣
⁣
When the breadcrumbs I was given of “healing” or “just wait and find the right drug combination” or “this takes time” or “you need to combine it with electro shock therapy” or “these drugs aren’t a cure all” or my favorite one: ⁣
⁣
“It’s not the drugs making you feel suicidal and crazy , it’s your genetic mental illness.” ⁣
⁣
Bruh..bruh..bruh.. ⁣
⁣
There’s a reason there’s a black box label on these drugs that say they can cause psychosis and suicidality….because they can cause psychosis and suicidality. ⁣
⁣
That’s some potent gaslighting going on, I think you may be a psychopath Big Pharma, to try and deny my lived experience and blame it on absolutely everything else other than what it really is….YOU. ⁣
⁣

⁣

⁣
Sorry people have lost their lives to your greed, insanity and abuse…their coffins closing with their families believing it was Suicide, mental illness, SIDS, a fluke, a sudden heart attack…all lies sealed with them in their graves now. ⁣
⁣
Sorry you have to run smear campaigns against us as survivors of your abuse as we try to warn others about you. ⁣
⁣
Sorry. ⁣

We survived. ⁣
⁣
But not sorry. ⁣

Your reign is ending. ⁣

In college suffering from anxiety I was prescribed Prozac and the belief that I had a chemical imbalance due to genetics was planted and set into my brain. ⁣
•The concept of a “chemical imbalance” has been debunked—it does not exist but was fraudulently used to sell the drugs. ⁣

Let’s talk about how lonely it is at the top when you’ve had to lie, cheat and connive to get there. ⁣

The Great Oz sits behind the control panel, with all of the levers and knobs and bells and whistles that help him manage his kingdom. ⁣
⁣
He paid a fortune for this system, to ensure he could maintain his power and his stature with the people who see him on the screen they put up every day, commanding people to fall in line or the Great Oz will come after them and destroy them. ⁣
⁣
He sits alone now at the control desk. ⁣
⁣
He used to be surrounded by friends and family. But his ploys, machinations and lies eventually caught up with him and one by one, people left his side. ⁣
⁣
“Fuck ‘em,” he says. “I don’t need anyone.” ⁣
⁣
Now he surrounds himself with people he pays to be around him, and lest they forget how much he does for them he constantly reminds them of his omnipotence—he can crush them if he wanted to and withdraw himself. He makes them dependent on him to ensure he will never be alone again. ⁣
⁣
So they all comply, bowing down to him, adoring him and praising him as if he were a God. ⁣
⁣
And the Wizard of Oz, the all powerful, the conqueror, the ruler, gets up from the control panel and his kingdom that exists entirely in his head. ⁣
⁣
He is tired.⁣
⁣
Tired of the lies, the games, the cons he constantly runs on others, but he knows no other way to survive. ⁣
